                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>The concentration will expose students to certain jobs available at all museums, like curators and registrars, and teach students important skills like how to raise money and communicate effectively. </p>
<p>“It’s really wonderful to be able to offer a sort of introduction to the museum field for undergraduates,” Price said. “It’s something that a lot of people aren’t aware of or just aren’t knowledgeable about.”</p>
